fm: EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode TelBLL_CM_LockInit( EBTSRV_CM_LockFuncType param ) {     EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_FAILURE;     bool ret_lock = false;  	if(eBTSRV_CM_LOCKTYPE_MAX <= param) 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Param Error"); 	    return ret; 	}  	if(NULL == telfunc_lockstsShm) 	{ 		//���L�������̐�����Open 		telfunc_lockstsShm = (BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo *)BT_Service_CreateShm((char*)BTSRV_CM_TEL_FUNC_LOCKINFO_PATH); 		 		if(NULL != telfunc_lockstsShm) 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Shared memory open success");  			//Lock��񐶐��iinit�ƃ}�b�s���O�j 			ret_lock = BT_Service_CreateLock(); 			 			//Lock���̃v���Z�X�ُ�I�����l�����A�������̃^�C�~���O�ŋ��L�������̓��e���`�F�b�N 			//�������̃R�[�����ƈ�v�����ꍇ�ɂ͋��L�������̓��e���N���A���� 			if(telfunc_lockstsShm->type == param) 			{ 				telfunc_lockstsShm->type = eBTSRV_CM_LOCKTYPE_NONE; 			} 			 			if(FALSE != ret_lock) 			{ 				ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 			} 		} 		else 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Shared memory open failed"); 		} 	} 	else 	{ 		//���L��������Open�ɂ͐����������ALock�̏������Ɏ��s�����ꍇ��z�� 		ret_lock = BT_Service_CreateLock();  		if(FALSE != ret_lock) 		{ 			ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 		} 	}     return ret;  }

EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode TelBLL_CM_LockGet(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo* param) {     EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_FAILURE;     int  ret_api;  	if(NULL == param) 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Param Error"); 	    return ret; 	}  	if(eBTSRV_CM_LOCKTYPE_MAX <= param->type) 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Param Error"); 	    return ret; 	}      	if((NULL != telfunc_lockstsShm) && (MAP_FAILED != telfunc_lockstsShm_lock)) 	{ 		if(telfunc_lockstsShm->type != param->type) 		{ 			ret_api = CL_LockNowait(telfunc_lockstsShm_lock); 			 			if(EINVAL == ret_api) 			{ 				BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockNowait is Param Error: retCode = %d", ret_api); 			} 			else if(EBUSY == ret_api) 			{ 				BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockNowait (EBUSY): retCode = %d", ret_api); 				ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_BUSY; 			} 			else 			{ 				BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockNowait success ");  				//���L��������Lock��񎯕ʎq�̏������� 				BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo data; 				memset(&data,0x00, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo)); 				data.type = param->type; 				BT_Service_writeShm(&data); 				ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 			} 		} 		else 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockNowait success (Already locked) "); 			ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 		} 	} 	else 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"error: initialize not complete"); 	}      return ret; }

EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode TelBLL_CM_LockRelease(EBTSRV_CM_LockFuncType param) {     EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_FAILURE;     int  ret_api; 	 	if(eBTSRV_CM_LOCKTYPE_MAX <= param) 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Param Error"); 	    return ret; 	}  	if((NULL != telfunc_lockstsShm) && (MAP_FAILED != telfunc_lockstsShm_lock)) 	{ 		if(telfunc_lockstsShm->type != param) 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"success: Not locked or already locked by another process"); 			ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 			return ret; 		} 	 		ret_api = CL_LockRelease(telfunc_lockstsShm_lock);  		if(EINVAL == ret_api) 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockRelease is Param Error"); 		} 		else 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockRelease success ");  			//���L��������Lock��񎯕ʎq���N���A 			BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo data; 			memset(&data,0x00, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo)); 			data.type = eBTSRV_CM_LOCKTYPE_NONE; 			BT_Service_writeShm(&data); 			ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 		} 	} 	else 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"error: initialize not complete"); 	}     return ret; }

void* BT_Service_CreateShm( char* shmPath ) {     int32_t fd = -1;     int32_t ret = -1;     void* addr = NULL;     bool bCreate = false;      // ���L�������̍쐬     fd = shm_open( shmPath, O_RDWR, 0777 );     if( fd < 0 ) {         // �����ݎ�         if (ENOENT == errno) {             // ����             fd = shm_open( shmPath, O_CREAT | O_RDWR, 0777 );             if( fd < 0 ) {                 return NULL;             }             bCreate = true;             // ���L�������̃T�C�Y�ύX             ret = ftruncate( fd, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo));             if( ret < 0) {                 return NULL;             }         } else {             return NULL;         }     }      // ���L���������v���Z�X�̉��z��ԂɃ}�b�s���O     addr = mmap( 0, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo), PROT_READ | PROT_WRITE, MAP_SHARED, fd, 0 );     if( addr == MAP_FAILED ) {         return NULL;     }      // �����������̓��������N���A����     if (bCreate) {         memset(addr,0x00, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo));     }      return addr; }

bool BT_Service_CreateLock(void) {     bool ret = false;     int ret_lock;     	if(MAP_FAILED == telfunc_lockstsShm_lock) 	{ 		/* Lock������ */ 		/* �v���Z�X�������� (�Ԃ�l  0:����  -1:�G���[) */ 		ret_lock = CL_LockProcessInit(); 		if(0 != ret_lock) 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockProcessInit is Error: retCode = %d", ret_lock); 			return ret; 		} 		else 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockProcessInit is Success: retCode = %d", ret_lock); 			ret = true; 		}  		// Lock ���}�b�s���O 		telfunc_lockstsShm_lock = CL_LockMap(LOCK_TEL_FUNC_SEM); //�\������LockID��ݒ� 		if(MAP_FAILED == telfunc_lockstsShm_lock) 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockMap is Error"); 			ret = false; 		} 		else 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"CL_LockMap is Success"); 			ret = true; 		} 	} 	else 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Already done"); 		ret = true; 	} 	 	return ret;  }
